🔪🥩 The BEST Italian Beef Collab of the YEAR is HERE!! 

@publicanquality x @publicanqualitybread x @mr.beefchicago is hosting The Ultimate Italian Beef Sandwich Pop-Up 🍴🏙️ 

825 W Fulton Market, Chicago, IL 60607

One Off Hospitality’s Chef @rob_levitt of Publican Quality Meats (as seen on @thebearfx!) and James Beard award-winning baker @gregwadebakes of Publican Quality Bread are putting together their talents for bread making and butchering 

This Saturday, September 9th and Sunday, September 10th, stop by, say hi, and taste a “Publican Quality” take on the classic Chicago sandwich, available both days starting at 11AM, while supplies last 🥩🔪

And only on Saturday, the one and only Chris Zucchero of @mr.beefchicago will join the crew to say hi & sling his official Mr. Beef merch on-site from 11AM to 2PM

🎂🥳🎉 1,000 POUNDS OF CHEESECAKE is waiting for you at the Taste of Chicago!

All thanks to @elischeesecake and their 43rd birthday at the event. Like the back of their shirts say “TASTY SINCE ’80!”

The cake is 450 lbs of cream cheese, 70 lbs of sugar, 50 lbs of sour cream, 25 lbs of chocolate chips, 63 lbs of Eli’s Shortbread Cookie Crust, 65 lbs of eggs, 2 lbs of vanilla, 25 lbs of cherry glaze, 100 lbs of old fashioned buttercream icing, 125 lbs of cookie dough, and 25 lbs of graham crackers 

📍Summer Dance Stage
11:00 AM: Enjoy entertainment from @thcchicago_ @hipletballerinas and @jessewhitetumblers 
12:30 PM: Celebratory cake cutting + cake served free to the public!

Anybody drooling yet?

Join them TODAY for their massive cheesecake, or tomorrow for more delicious treats mentioned abo
ve!

One of my favorite things this year was seeing Dennis Watkins @themagicparlour 

🪄 As a 3rd generation magician, he grew up learning at his grandfather’s small storefront magic shop in Dallas, TX

Grab a drink at the cocktail bar and sit down for an evening of child-like wonder 💭
